dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Contour interval 10 feet." In upper margin: Topography. Text on verso: Description of the topographic map of the United States. "Triangulation by U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey. Topography by C.C. Vermeule. Surveyed in 1885. Culture revised 1904 ... " Historic Maps copy 1 mounted on cloth.
